## Katana Universal Commands

The following universal commands are available via the Katana MCP server:

- **katana-decompose**: Decompose a parent doc into children
- **katana-work**: Start working a task
- **katana-board**: Show the kanban board
- **katana-validate**: Validate a document

For detailed command configuration, see [`.katana/agents-manifest.json`]({{manifestPath}}).
